Quickstrike:



Quickstrike found a catch. It was easy for him to take down. It was 
one of those ground dwelling creatures, about medium size. Since his 
long and flat body made it easy to go in underground dens, it was 
fast.

No one had called for him, asking him where he was, so he went on. He 
followed the forest, using his navigational systems to find the 
direction of the bunker.
